      <property name="cache-location"
                version="0.8"
                writable="1"
                construct-only="1"
                transfer-ownership="none"
                getter="get_cache_location"
                default-value="NULL">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="src/lib/clapper/clapper-media-item.c"
             line="1075">Media downloaded cache file location.

This can be either set for newly created media items or
it will be updated after download is completed if
[property@Clapper.Player:download-enabled] is set.

NOTE: This property was added in 0.8 as write at construct only.
It can also be read only since Clapper 0.10.</doc>
        <type name="utf8" c:type="gchar*"/>
      </property>
      <property name="container-format"
                deprecated="1"
                deprecated-version="0.10"
