      <glib:signal name="download-complete"
                   when="last"
                   no-recurse="1"
                   no-hooks="1"
                   version="0.8">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="src/lib/clapper/clapper-player.c"
             line="3024">Media was fully downloaded to local cache directory. This signal will
be only emitted when progressive download buffering is enabled by
setting [property@Clapper.Player:download-enabled] property to %TRUE.

Download cache file location can also be read directly from @item
through its [property@Clapper.MediaItem:cache-location] property.</doc>
